@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rcrelm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos(((v1 + 0.56 + v2 + 0.49) / 0.13))
    v2 = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.34) * wp.sin(tmp + 0.41)) / v1)
    v1 = v1
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.75) / (v2 + 0.95 - v2 + 0.89)) + ((v1 + 0.82 + v0 + 0.70) + 0.26))
    data[tid] = v0
